query:
INSERT INTO checklistItemResults (taskChecklistId, templateItemId, result, createdAt)
SELECT 
  tc.id as taskChecklistId,
  cti.id as templateItemId,
  'fail' as result,
  NOW() as createdAt
FROM taskChecklists tc
JOIN checklistTemplateItems cti ON cti.templateId = tc.templateId
WHERE tc.status = 'failed'
LIMIT 3;
